HEADWORD: Savagism
<hw>Sav"a*gism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The state of being
savage; the state of rude, uncivilized men, or of men in their native
wildness and rudeness.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

